\begin_layout Section
Installation using the Installer
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
With SLiMS Meranti, in addition to the manual installation (the first way),
 installation can also be performed using the SLiMS Installer features.
 The steps to use the SLiMS installer are:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Create a database
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Create a username and password for the database 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Call SLiMS with a webbrowser, e.g 
\begin_inset Flex URL
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://localhost/slims-slims5/
\end_layout

\end_inset

, then the browser will automatically redirect to
\begin_inset Flex URL
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://localhost/slims-slims5/install/index.php
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

